snippet.title: Monster Hunter Online - Expansion 2.0 Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Expansion 2.0 of Monster Hunter Online! Expansion 2.0 will go live on June 28th!

New monsters include;
Flame Blangonga
Lavasioth
White Monoblos
Gravios
Infernal Tartaronis
Slicemargl Subspecies
New forms of Merphistophelin
Rajang
And Chameleos!
